  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a MariaDB</title>

    <para>
      <application>MariaDB</application> is a community-developed fork and a
drop-in replacement for the <application>MySQL</application> relational
database management system.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

